<section id="about" class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
        <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12 lg:mb-16" data-aos="fade-up">
            <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-display font-bold mb-4 lg:mb-6">
                About <span class="gradient-text-primary">Unimanage Technologies</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-600">
                Empowering fitness businesses across India with cutting-edge technology solutions
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-center">
            <div data-aos="fade-right">
                <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 lg:mb-6">Our Mission</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 lg:mb-6">
                    We're dedicated to providing fitness businesses in India with the tools they need to thrive in the digital age. Our comprehensive gym management software streamlines operations while our web development services create powerful online presences that attract and retain members.
                </p>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 lg:mb-8">
                    With over a decade of experience in both fitness management and web technologies, we understand the unique challenges faced by gym owners and fitness professionals across India. Our solutions are designed to save time, increase revenue, and enhance member experiences for fitness businesses of all sizes.
                </p>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 lg:gap-6">
                    <div class="bg-white p-4 lg:p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md">
                        <div class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold gradient-text-primary mb-2">500+</div>
                        <div class="text-gray-600">Happy Clients</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white p-4 lg:p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md">
                        <div class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold gradient-text-secondary mb-2">10+</div>
                        <div class="text-gray-600">Years Experience</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 lg:gap-6" data-aos="fade-left">
                <article class="bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-50 to-orange-100 p-6 lg:p-8 rounded-2xl">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 lg:w-16 lg:h-16 gradient-primary rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 lg:mb-6">
                        <i class="fas fa-dumbbell text-white text-xl lg:text-2xl" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-lg lg:text-xl font-bold mb-2 lg:mb-3">Gym Management</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm lg:text-base">Comprehensive software to manage memberships, classes, trainers, and billing for Indian fitness centers.</p>
                </article>

                <article class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-blue-100 p-6 lg:p-8 rounded-2xl">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 lg:w-16 lg:h-16 gradient-secondary rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 lg:mb-6">
                        <i class="fas fa-laptop-code text-white text-xl lg:text-2xl" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-lg lg:text-xl font-bold mb-2 lg:mb-3">Web Development</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm lg:text-base">Professional websites and web applications tailored to your fitness brand in India.</p>
                </article>

                <article class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-green-100 p-6 lg:p-8 rounded-2xl">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 lg:w-16 lg:h-16 gradient-accent rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 lg:mb-6">
                        <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt text-white text-xl lg:text-2xl" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-lg lg:text-xl font-bold mb-2 lg:mb-3">Mobile Apps</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm lg:text-base">Custom mobile applications for member engagement and management for Indian fitness businesses.</p>
                </article>

                <article class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-purple-100 p-6 lg:p-8 rounded-2xl">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 lg:w-16 lg:h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-purple-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 lg:mb-6">
