                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-lg lg:text-xl font-bold mb-2 lg:mb-3">Analytics</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm lg:text-base">Data-driven insights to optimize your business performance in the Indian fitness market.</p>
                </article>
            </div>
